TP Tool is a MATLAB toolbox for tensor product model transformation based controller design

requirements:
	MATLAB (at least R14)
	YALMIP
	LMI solver for YALMIP (recommended: SeDuMi or Robust Control Toolbox)
license:
	see LICENSE file
more information:
	http://tptool.sztaki.hu


directories:

example:
	example usage of the toolbox on different controller design problems
array:
	functions related to multidimensional array manipulations
hull:
	functions related to polytopic model generation (convex hull)
lmi:
	functions related to linear matrix inequalities
lpv:
	lpv model representation, sampling and hosvd
util:
	miscellaneous utilities
